ool and I heard the key in the door and someone walk in. I assumed it was him but it was the cleaning staff (maybe returning to the scene of the crime!?) and they questioned me as to why I had not checked out of the hotel...our checkout day was not for several more days. The most annoying part is that she did not even knock..just walked right in. The hotel is fine if you want a springbreak / lowclass experience but otherwise I would not recomend this hotel to anyone unless that is what you are looking for and if you also don't mind being treated like an annoyance if something godforbid happens to you at the hotel like me.	
