se. Palms definately offers fast paced, no time to sit and order a movie on the tv kind of stay. PS the beds are the most wonderful thing in the world! I have NEVER slept in such a wonderful bed ever! And,, you can actually call housekeeping and they will tell you the company that makes them. Now THATS service!!!	
