e and said he would send someone to look at the a/c and would credit me with two sodas from the fridge. Well, no one came to look at the a/c, and he never followed up, and he didn't credit the sodas either. I was also told that there were a lot of celebrities there, I didn't see one. I did see Robert Thompson, the announcer from Celebrity Poker Showdown and he was very nice. Oh yeah, on Friday, at about 9:00 am, they started blasting music from the pool area and that I did hear from the room I had on the 27th floor. All in all, I could take it or leave it.	
